      "description": "Eclipse JDT Language Server with Spring Boot language extension. Adds IntelliSense, Go-to-Definition, refactoring, diagnostics, and Spring-specific features (application.yml autocomplete, @RequestMapping hints, bean references) for .java, application.properties, application.yml, pom.xml, and build.gradle.",
